message:
Fact #17 What is Sex Trafficking?  Sex trafficking is when a commercial sex act is induced by force, fraud, or coercion, or in which the person induced to perform such act has not attained 18 years of age.
30 Facts ~ National Slavery and Human Trafficking Prevention Month #Awareness #Prevention #Education
